Constructs the Index with the namespace resources, equivalence resources, protein family resource, named complex resource, and gene scaffolding resource.

Parameters:
adResources - List of ResourceLocation, the annotation definition resource locations
nsResources - List of ResourceLocation, the namespace resource locations
eqResources - List of Equivalence, the equivalence resource locations
pfResource - ResourceLocation, the protein family resource
ncResource - ResourceLocation, the named complex resource
gsResource - ResourceLocation, the gene scaffolding resource
orthoResources - Set of ResourceLocation, the orthology resources
